#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.20/guides/scripting.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Note: JBang debugging always suspends thus you need to connect the debugger to have the application run."
msgstr "注意：JBang 调试时程序会始终暂停，因此您需要连接调试器才能让应用程序运行。"

